{"tid":2036932,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［制裁近了］美參議員提新制裁法案 針對損港人權自由官員資金","createTime":"2020-05-26T18:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T20:39:57.000Z","uid":239336,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"071c142c02253c96c01848eba088fe66ab69e011","tid":2036932,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:02:31.000Z","msg":"美國國會亦十分關注全國人大有關「港版國安法」的決定草案。兩名參議員上周已即時提出新制裁法案，提案人之一的共和黨參議員圖米（Pat Toomey）接受《蘋果》訪問時批評，中共加速並有系統地否定對港人基本人權保障的承諾，提及有過千人在反政府示威中被捕、15名民主派知名人士被高調拘捕，形容「港版國安法」令人憂慮香港的人權及自由勢遭剝奪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200527/60984747%20%20/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200527%2F60984747%2520%2520%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA7Tr7UizNwCuyTydxCoZ6r4%3D&h=5f695d1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200527%2F60984747%2520%2520%2F&h=a4249a8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20200527/60984747%20%20/</a><br />\n<br />\n快啲亮劍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8fab6b477ebab6523fc07595ae6eb1b0fd6fd8","tid":2036932,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"上年咪整咗把劍，依加又整多把做乜春，肯用未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b6fa19b3041d4c695961f360fb504f85588841","tid":2036932,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:06:26.000Z","msg":"快啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a3a1e2ffeea9ce3428904ef68dbe579d514436","tid":2036932,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"4a8fab6b477ebab6523fc07595ae6eb1b0fd6fd8","tid":2036932,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"上年咪整咗把劍，依加又整多把做乜春，肯用未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:10:50.000Z","msg":"美國係咁 開波前一定好多議案<br />\n因為要為將來做既野提供合法性<br />\n雖然唔知邊條會拎黎用<br />\n總之立左先<br />\n下個月用唔定 下年又唔定 可能10年後又唔定"},{"pid":"ea782c8795d832c6db4674e9078b39fb8f729d33","tid":2036932,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:33.000Z","msg":"本身有magnitsky act 可以隨時用"},{"pid":"6bb5356d7e21d6e01f2184bb1ea67f614093f0ab","tid":2036932,"uid":33904,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"4a8fab6b477ebab6523fc07595ae6eb1b0fd6fd8","tid":2036932,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:03:37.000Z","msg":"上年咪整咗把劍，依加又整多把做乜春，肯用未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"呢把利好多，金融核彈黎。<br />\n<br />\n上一把淨係斬官員同定期review香港自治程度，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呢把針對埋同d狗官有業務既銀行</span>，<br />\n即係恆生、匯豐、中銀個d，<br />\n一出手全滅，對香港同支那打擊可以係毀滅性。<br />\n<br />\n美國以往都制裁過支那既銀行，<br />\n原理係咁：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「被拒絕進入美國金融體系」之所以具有威懾力是因為&mdash;&mdash;目前國際通行的結算系統是美國主導的，美元也是最主要的國際結算貨幣。「被拒絕進入美國金融體系」意味着被處罰銀行不得使用美元進行交易和結算，基本相當於從國際金融系統中清除出去。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">令一間銀行用唔到美金，其實即係佢佢執撚柒去。</span>"},{"pid":"007684c2e254da0dba381535b718c9564a76b0ca","tid":2036932,"uid":33028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T18:20:24.000Z","msg":"之前嗰啲法案授權總統承認香港西藏獨立其實都係多餘，因為總統本身有權承認任何國家，70年代同中共建交都唔需要國會授權。所以其實都係做下樣。"},{"pid":"7415b3f99e4f3ba601cf30230167231ccbebb82e","tid":2036932,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:14:33.000Z","msg":"姐係借錢比選舉主任同強姦犯買樓的銀行都中招"},{"pid":"acdb25377b017f7377f16eaefa65d6c6e89a97b9","tid":2036932